{"tid":1574310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「心理準備」其實比中共管治無想像中咁恐怖⋯","createTime":"2019-09-16T11:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T12:48:20.000Z","uid":67294,"like":16,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2ceed80761c99fbf13c60cd4e46f9486c45bbfa2","tid":1574310,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:02:17.000Z","msg":"依家大陸無以前咁落後，好多大型商場搞線下活動<br />\n支付寶勁方便真係唔洗戴錢包，野食衛生有啲仲乾淨過香港<br />\n最緊要啲野好食又抵<br />\n<br />\n平時娛樂唔止得一個電視台，仲有BAT三巨頭整勁多偽韓綜睇<br />\n網上言論自由其實無想像中咁差, 基本上你唔怕可以用縮寫傾敏感題目<br />\n<br />\n同埋只要你唔觸犯到中共底線，好多時系統己經自己幫你del左，唔會下下都有公安上門（認真，你係公安都廢事煩啦）<br />\n<br />\n就算係被中共管治，只要你聽聽話話其實生活質素可以比依家更好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所以唔好煩啦，港共快手出解放軍實彈鎮壓再取消變一國一制啦，我準備好了</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a83e471079f886d592d3fec0bab3ff4efa9eed0","tid":1574310,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:04:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=5f8acf18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyo